title: Quicken Deluxe 2009 Un-Touched (Original)
description:
Quicken Deluxe 2009

Quicken Deluxe makes managing your personal finances easy by allowing you to view all of your information in one place, so you gain a big-picture view that helps you track just how your money gets spent. Set savings goals, then monitor your finances by month to see just how much you're actually saving. Track your bills to see which ones have been paid and which are coming due, and add reminders to your Google or Outlook calendar so you never miss a payment. Quicken Deluxe 2009 also makes it easier for you to prepare for tax season by helping you capture all possible deductible expenses and allowing you to export your financial data directly into TurboTax (not included). With the insights you'll gain into your personal finances, you'll find new ways to save so you can spend more money on the things you and your family really want.

Features

    * Bring together your personal financial information in one place so you can more closely monitor your spending habits
    * Connect to your various online banking accounts, credit cards and brokerage sites with a single convenient password
    * Simplify your financial planning and budgeting process by setting savings goals and monitoring your progress month by month
    * Capture all possible deductible expenses to save time during tax season
    * Never miss a bill, stay on top of bills due and paid and add reminders to your Google or Outlook calendar all from one place (Sync to Calendar feature available via patch release in late October 2008; Outlook export requires Outlook 2003 or 2007)
    * Export your data directly to TurboTax (not included) for speedy tax preparation.
